---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="System Stories Â· Real Problems, Systematic Solutions"
    description="Case studies of founder-built internal systems: dashboards, backend platforms, and operational tools that solve real business problems."
>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="section-wide">
            <h1 class="text-center mb-24">System Stories</h1>
            <p class="text-large text-center mb-64" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
                Real problems, systematic solutions, documented outcomes.
            </p>

            <div class="card-grid">
                <!-- Story 1 -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="mono" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;">Dashboard System</div>
                    <h3>Replacing Manual Reporting</h3>
                    <p class="mb-24">
                        A SaaS founder was spending 4 hours daily merging data from 5 different spreadsheets to understand business performance.
                    </p>
                    <div class="mb-24">
                        <span class="tag">Dashboard</span>
                        <span class="tag">Automation</span>
                        <span class="tag">Reporting</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 24px;">
                        <div style="color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">Outcome</div>
                        <div style="color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 500;">Daily reporting time reduced from 4 hours to 10 minutes</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Story 2 -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="mono" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;">Backend Platform</div>
                    <h3>Operations Automation System</h3>
                    <p class="mb-24">
                        An e-commerce operator was manually processing orders across 3 platforms, leading to errors and customer service issues.
                    </p>
                    <div class="mb-24">
                        <span class="tag">API Integration</span>
                        <span class="tag">Workflow Automation</span>
                        <span class="tag">Error Handling</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 24px;">
                        <div style="color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">Outcome</div>
                        <div style="color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 500;">Order processing automated, errors reduced by 92%</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Story 3 -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="mono" style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;">Internal Tool</div>
                    <h3>Client Onboarding Portal</h3>
                    <p class="mb-24">
                        A service business was using 8 different tools for client onboarding, causing confusion and delays.
                    </p>
                    <div class="mb-24">
                        <span class="tag">Portal</span>
                        <span class="tag">Document Management</span>
                        <span class="tag">Notifications</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 24px;">
                        <div style="color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">Outcome</div>
                        <div style="color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 500;">Onboarding time reduced from 2 weeks to 3 days</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-64">
                <p class="mb-24" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">
                    These are anonymized examples. Real stories include more detail about challenges and solutions.
                </p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Describe Your Challenge</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
